# Forbidden Planning Patterns

- Business logic inside UI
- Direct `SharedPreferences` usage in widgets or domain
- Tight persistence coupling in presentation
- Shared mutable state outside StateNotifiers
- Generic abstractions without need
- Oversized providers
- Monolithic repositories
- Missing error/empty states
- Ignoring platform service cleanup
- Ignoring ADHD-friendly animation timing

